description: Rimworld output log published using HugsLib

this is the main python scrip for my build of fieldstation 42 github project this code is for using 3 button power, channel up, and channel down. The system starts in a low-power-mode showing fs42 on the TM1637 LED display. The system also has Diagnostic menu that can be used to set the system date and time or sync to a network. The menu is accessed by holding down the channel down and channel up buttons at the same time for 5 seconds
